data.description: Introducing 5481 Roosevelt Loop NE, a stunning residence nestled in the heart of Rio Rancho, NM.. This meticulously maintained home, built in 2006, exudes pride in ownership at every turn, offering a rare blend of comfort, style, and convenience in over 2000 square feet. This home offers easy access to NM 550 for easy commuting to Santa Fe, Los Alamos, and other northern locations, as well as Albuquerque, the Jemez Mountains and more.As you approach, you'll be greeted by the charm of a curved solid hardwood door. The exterior boasts a newer roof and stucco, ensuring durability and curb appeal for years to come, while the xeriscaped front and back yards enhance the low-maintenance lifestyle.
